attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a robot. They begin by attaching the wheels to the wheel unit, then the neck to the base. The head is attached to the neck, and the student removes the camera caps before inserting the batteries into the battery box. The student lifts the navvis' base and then removes the batteries from the box before removing the navvi's head. The student then disassembles the neck and puts it in the box before disassembling the base wheels and putting the wheels and base
